    "long_instructions": "### Alex's Version\r\n\r\nAlex wants to recreate the intro to Wake Me Up by Aloe Blacc using the shadow blocks in the workspace:\r\n\r\n> I noticed that there are 4 tracks that all repeat, so I can use 4 separate loops to recreate this timeline.\r\n\r\n![](https://images.code.org/9140c454f9d4dd31fd4cfed90de2085c-image-1745259492284.png)\r\n\r\nTo make sense of the timeline, Alex broke it down into four separate track sequences and worked on each one individually.\r\n\r\n**Your task:** Use **decomposition** to break the remix into four smaller parts - one for each repeating track. For each part, build a loop that matches its pattern. Then combine them to reconstruct the full timeline. Your final version should look and sound like the original, just with cleaner code.\r\n",
    "predict_settings": {
      "isPredictLevel": false
    },
